# Faithful Path — catatan dev & deploy

**Production (domain):** https://app.talaqee.com/  
**CMS admin:** https://app.talaqee.com/admin.html  
**API tes:** https://app.talaqee.com/api/cms/public/health.php  
**MySQL:** `host.docker.internal` (di Docker) · database/user: `alquran` · config: `api/config.local.php`  
