Build: `npm run build` (`.env.production`) → upload `dist/`, `api/`, `router.php`

## Docker (production — PHP 8.2)

**Penyebab error 404 CMS:** perintah `-t /app/dist` hanya melayani frontend. Folder **`api/`** ada di `/app/api/`, bukan di `dist/`.

### Struktur di VPS (`/var/www/html/alquran`)

```
alquran/
  router.php
  dist/          ← hasil npm run build
  api/           ← PHP CMS + subscription
  api/config.local.php
```

### Perintah docker run (perbaikan)

```bash
# SALAH — /api/* → 404:
docker run -d -p 80:80 -v /var/www/html/alquran:/app --name alquran jibas \
  php -S 0.0.0.0:80 -t /app/dist

# BENAR — pakai router.php di root /app:
docker stop alquran && docker rm alquran

docker run -d -p 80:80 \
  -v /var/www/html/alquran:/app \
  --add-host=host.docker.internal:host-gateway \
  --name alquran jibas \
  php -S 0.0.0.0:80 -t /app /app/router.php
```

### Atau docker compose (disarankan)

```bash
cd /var/www/html/alquran
docker compose up -d --build
```

### MySQL dari dalam container

Di `api/config.local.php` di server, host DB = IP host (bukan `127.0.0.1`):

```php
putenv('DB_HOST=host.docker.internal');  // atau IP VPS, mis. 172.17.0.1
```

Lalu di container: `php api/sync-mysql.php`

### Rekaman Talaqqi (Docker / production)

Rekaman memakai **API PHP** di `api/talaqqi/` — **tidak wajib** `npm run talaqqi:chat` di server.

1. Upload folder `api/talaqqi/` (termasuk `ping.php`, `uploads/` writable)
2. `router.php` aktif: `php -S 0.0.0.0:80 -t /app /app/router.php`
3. `api/config.local.php`: `DB_HOST=db` (docker compose) atau `host.docker.internal`
4. Build dengan `VITE_TALAQQI_API_BASE=https://app.talaqee.com/api/talaqqi` di `.env.production`
5. Tes: `https://app.talaqee.com/api/talaqqi/ping.php` → `{"ok":true,...}`
6. `docker compose exec alquran php /app/api/sync-mysql.php` (tabel `recordings`, `comments`)

Volume uploads: `api/talaqqi/uploads` (docker-compose sudah mount).

