### Deploy https://app.talaqee.com

```bash
cd /var/www/html/alquran
# Upload api/config.local.php (DB_HOST=host.docker.internal, DB_USER=alquran, DB_NAME=alquran)
npm run build   # di laptop, .env.production → https://app.talaqee.com
# upload dist/

docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d --build
docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml exec alquran php /app/api/sync-mysql.php
```

**Nginx Proxy Manager:** Proxy Host  
- Domain: `app.talaqee.com`  
- Forward: container PHP (internal)  
- SSL: Let's Encrypt ON  

**Penting:** Di `api/config.local.php` untuk Docker pakai `DB_HOST=host.docker.internal`, **bukan** IP publik VPS.

